 The Lord resists the proud; but he gives grace to the humble. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 35.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  The wise shall inherit glory; but the ungodly have exalted their own dishonor. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 1.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Hear, ye children, the instruction of a father, and attend to know understanding. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 2.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 For I give you a good gift; forsake ye not my law. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 3.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For I also was a son obedient to my father, and loved in the sight of my mother: }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 4.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  who spoke and instructed me, saying, Let our speech be fixed in thine heart, keep our commandments, forget them not: }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 5.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  and do not neglect the speech of my mouth. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 6.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And forsake it not, and it shall cleave to thee: love it, and it shall keep thee. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 7.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Secure it, and it shall exalt thee: honor it, that it may embrace thee; }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 8.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 that it may give unto thy head a crown of graces, and may cover thee with a crown of delight. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 9.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 Hear, my son, and receive my words; and the years of thy life shall be increased, that the resources of thy life may be many. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 10.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 For I teach thee the ways of wisdom; and I cause thee to go in right paths. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 11.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 For when thou goest, thy steps shall not be straitened; and when thou runnest, thou shalt not be distressed. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 12.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 Take hold of my instruction; let it not go, -- but keep it for thyself for thy life. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 13.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Go not in the ways of the ungodly, neither covet the ways of transgressors. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 14.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  In whatever place they shall pitch their camp, go not thither; but turn from them, and pass away. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 15.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For they cannot sleep, unless they have done evil: their sleep is taken away, and they rest not. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 16.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For these live upon the b
read of ungodliness, and are drunken with wine of transgression. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 17.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  But the ways of the righteous shine like light; they go on and shine, until the day be fully come. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 18.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  But the ways of the ungodly are dark; they know not how they stumble. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 19.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  My son, at
tend to my speech; and apply thine ear to my words: }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 20.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  that thy fountains may not fail thee; keep them in thine heart. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 21.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For they are life to those that find them, and health to all their flesh. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 22.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Keep thine heart with the utmost care; for out of thes
e are the issues of life. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 23.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Remove from thee a forward mouth, and put far away from thee unjust lips. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 24.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Let thine eyes look right on, and let thine eyelids assent to just things. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 25.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Make straight paths for thy feet, and order thy ways aright. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 26.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Turn
 not aside to the right hand nor to the left, but turn away thy foot from an evil way: [for God knows the ways on the right hand, but those on the left are crooked:] and he will make thy ways straight, and will guide thy steps in peace. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 
