\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For where ten yoke of oxen plough [the land] shall yield one jar-full, and he that sows six homers shall produce three measures. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 11.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
