\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 16.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Let not waters out of thy fountain be spilt by thee, but let thy waters go into thy streets. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 17.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
