hy friend, thou shalt deliver thine hand to an enemy. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 2.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For a man's own lips become a strong snare to him, and he is caught with the lips of his own mouth. }{
