 This is the genealogy of men in the day in which God made Adam; in the image of God he made him: }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 2.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 male and female he made them, and blessed them; and he called his name Adam, in the day in which he made them. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 3.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Adam lived two hundred and thirty yea
rs, and begot a son after his own form and after his own image, and he called his name Seth. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 4.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 And the days of Adam, which he lived after his begetting Seth, were seven hundred years; and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 5.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the days of Adam which he l
ived were nine hundred and thirty years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 6.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Now Seth lived two hundred and five years, and begot Enos. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 7.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Seth lived after his begetting Enos, seven hundred and seven years, and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 8.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the days of Seth were
 nine hundred and twelve years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 9.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Enos lived an hundred and ninety years, and begot Cainan. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 10.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Enos lived after his begetting Cainan, seven hundred and fifteen and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 11.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the days of Enos were nine h
undred and five years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 12.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Cainan lived an hundred and seventy years, and he begot Maleleel. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 13.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Cainan lived after his begetting Maleleel, seven hundred and forty years, and he begot son and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 14.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the days of Cainan w
ere nine hundred and ten years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 15.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Maleleel lived an hundred and sixty and five years, and he begot Jared. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 16.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Maleleel lived after his begetting Jared, seven hundred and thirty years, and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 17.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the 
days of Maleleel were eight hundred and ninety and five years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 18.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Jared lived an hundred and two years, and begot Enoch: }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 19.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  and Jared lived after his begetting Enoch, eight hundred years, and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 20.}{
\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And all the days of Jared were nine hundred and sixty and two years, and he died. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 21.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 And Enoch lived an hundred and sixty and five years, and begat Mathusala. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 22.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 And Enoch was well-pleasing to God after his begetting Mathusala, two hundred years, and he begot sons and daughters. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 23.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 And all the days of Enoch were three hundred and sixty and five years. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 24.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And Enoch was well-pleasing to God, and was not found, because God translated him. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 
