{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And the Lord God having seen that the wicked actions of men were multiplied upon the earth, and that every one in his heart was intently brooding over evil continually, }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 7.}{
