 For the value of a harlot is as much as of one loaf; and a woman hunts for the precious souls of men. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 27.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Shall any one bind fire in his bosom, and not burn his garments? }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 28.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  or will any one walk on coals of fire, and not burn his feet? }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 29.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 So is he that goes in to a married woman; he shall not be held guiltless, neither any one that touches her. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 30.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 It is not to be wondered at if one should be taken stealing, for he steals that when hungry he may satisfy his soul: }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 31.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 but if he should be taken, he shall repay sevenfold, and shall deliver himself by giving all his goods. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 32.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 But the adulterer through want of sense procures destruction to his soul. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 33.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  He endures both pain and disgrace, and his reproach shall never be wiped off. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 34.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  For the soul of her husband is full of jealousy: he will not spare in the day of vengeance. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 35.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
 He will not forego his enmity for any ransom: neither will he be reconciled for many gifts. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 1.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  My son, keep my words, and hide with thee my commandments. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 2.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  My son, honor the Lord, and thou shalt be strong; and fear none but him; keep my commandments, and thou shalt live; and keep my words as the pupils of thine eyes. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 3.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  And bind them on thy fingers, and write them on the table of thine heart. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 4.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789 
