 that she may keep thee from the strange and wicked woman, if she should assail thee with flattering words. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid12399789\charrsid12399789 24.}{\cs31\f35\fs32\insrsid12399789  Now then, my son, hearken to me, and attend to the 
